{# Default memory-context template (v12 M7 Task 7.6).

Renders retrieved memory entries as a bulleted list. Each entry shows
the creation date (UTC, YYYY-MM-DD), the source tool (or `unknown`),
and the text truncated to `max_entry_chars` codepoints.

Inputs:
    entries        - iterable of MemoryEntry
    entry_count    - optional integer; if 0/absent the template emits
                     nothing so the PromptAssembler can drop the
                     section entirely.
    max_entry_chars - optional integer; default 280.

User-supplied fields (`text`, `source_tool`) are passed through Jinja2's
`e` filter to prevent template injection.
#}
{% set count = entry_count | default(entries | length) %}
{% if count > 0 %}
## Relevant memory ({{ count }} entr{{ "y" if count == 1 else "ies" }})

{% for entry in entries %}
- {{ entry.created_at.strftime('%Y-%m-%d') }} · {{ (entry.source_tool or 'unknown') | e }}: {{ (entry.text[:(max_entry_chars | default(280))]) | e }}{% if entry.text | length > (max_entry_chars | default(280)) %}…{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
